Prompt-system files

This is where the repo becomes actually useful for your art stack.

prompt_templates.md

Have templates like:

1. Naturalist macro

[species] in its [lifecycle_stage] phase, growing on [substrate], with [surface_traits], [shape_language], [color_range], extreme macro photography, shallow depth of field, micro-forest scale, spore dust, condensation, documentary realism

2. Maximalist mutation

A colossal [species] interpreted as [architectural/fashion/alien object], combining [stage_1] and [stage_2], with [texture_tags], [motion_tags], [palette], recursive branching, biomorphic excess, wet iridescence, catastrophic detail density

3. Mathy bio-network

Use [species] plasmodial vein logic as a routing system across [surface], with oscillating cytoplasmic flow, graph-theoretic branching, pulse propagation, adaptive maze behavior, rendered as living topology

4. Slug procession

Cellular slime mold aggregation streams converging into a migrating slug, tiny amoebae forming a unified body, soil-particle scale, ritual procession energy, soft translucency, emergent intelligence made visible

